 full-screen mode, if not already there.'}.		{'full screen off' . { self . #fullScreenOff} . 'if in full-screen mode, takes you out of it.'}.		nil.		{'set display depth...' . {self. #setDisplayDepth} . 'choose how many bits per pixel.'}.		{'set desktop color...' . {self. #changeBackgroundColor} . 'choose a uniform color to use as desktop background.'}.	}! !